001package andesite.event;
002
003import andesite.NodeState;
004import andesite.player.AndesitePlayer;
005
006import javax.annotation.Nonnegative;
007import javax.annotation.Nonnull;
008import javax.annotation.Nullable;
009
010public interface AndesiteEventListener {
011    default void onPlayerCreated(@Nonnull NodeState state, @Nonnull String userId,
012                                 @Nonnull String guildId, @Nonnull AndesitePlayer player) {}
013    
014    default void onPlayerDestroyed(@Nonnull NodeState state, @Nonnull String userId,
015                                   @Nonnull String guildId, @Nonnull AndesitePlayer player) {}
016    
017    default void onWebSocketClosed(@Nonnull NodeState state, @Nonnull String userId,
018                                   @Nonnull String guildId, @Nonnegative int closeCode,
019                                   @Nullable String reason, boolean byRemote) {}
020}
